# Sculpture in Data — Windsurf Rules

## Identity
App name: Sculpture in Data
Tagline: How sculpture evolved — materials, movements, geography, and lineages since 1800

## Fonts (non-negotiable)
Display/headlines: Fraunces (Google Fonts, variable, serif)
Body/UI/axes: DM Sans (Google Fonts, sans-serif)
Load via next/font/google in layout.tsx. Never use Inter, Roboto, Arial, or system fonts.

