All values MUST come from CSS variables or Tailwind config. Never hardcode hex in components.

bg-primary: #FAFAF9 (warm off-white)
bg-secondary: #F0F1EE (cards)
bg-sidebar: #1A1D1C (sidebar background, also network graph dark contexts)
text-primary: #1A1D1C
text-secondary: #5C6560
text-tertiary: #6B706D (WCAG AA safe — 4.5:1 on bg-primary)
