## Sidebar
Dark variant: bg-sidebar (#1A1D1C) background.
Text: sidebar-text (#FAFAF9), muted: sidebar-text-muted (#9CA3A0).
Active nav item: sidebar-text + 3px left border in accent-primary + accent-muted-dark bg.
No right border — dark/light contrast defines the edge.

## Charts
No borders or boxes. Charts float in whitespace.
Gridlines: horizontal only, border-grid color, ~0.3 opacity.
Axes: left + bottom only, border-axis color.
Labels: text-tertiary, 0.75rem.
Direct labels on data > legends whenever possible.
Tooltips: minimal, no border, subtle shadow, bg-primary background.
Transitions: 400ms ease-out.

